








Post request: {
    conditionals: 
    1. login functionality: if the user name and password == a username and password already in the database, then we want to route to that users homepage.
    if the user name or password don't alreadt exist, then we throw an error => "check again or create an account"
    2. sign up functionality: if the username and password == a username and password already in the database, throw an error => "choose a new username". 
    if they don't, then append to the database
}